This is your story come true... Your journey of marriage begins with "I Do". Cherish this bond, it belongs to only the two of you. Start each day with gratitude and compassion for each other, and unconditional love will follow. Believe in each other; support each other's dreams. Remember to dream together too. Always give more than you think the other needs. Say "I love you" and "thank you" every day! Trust, respect, and appreciate each other. Be spontaneous, be fun, be romantic! Stand together, but let there be space in your togetherness. Know when to listen, to talk, to let your heart feel. Apologize. Forgive and forget - doing so will make you feel better! Work together. Play together. Pray together. Allow God to be the foundation of your marriage. You have been chosen for each other... it is His plan. With each passing year, you will grow closer together, drawing strength from each other... and two shall become one. Beautiful print with multiple frame selections to choose from. Choose a rustic old farmhouse Tobacco Lath Frame to match the brown wood tones and the background of this print. Or choose more of a modern farmhouse look with a White Washed Frame or a Gray Washed Frame, both of which come with a keyhole opening on the back for easy hanging. The Black Frame option will give you a bit more of an upscale feel while still being very affordable. Our Father which art in heaven,
Hallowed be thy name.
Thy kingdom come.
Thy will be done in earth,
as it is in heaven.
Give us this day our daily bread.
And forgive us our debts,
as we forgive our debtors.
And lead us not into temptation,
but deliver us from evil:
For thine is the kingdom,
and the power, and the glory, for ever.
    Amen
